## Command Reference

### Development Commands

```bash
# Start Storybook dev server
npm run start

# Build Stencil components
npm run build:ci

# Build Storybook static
npm run build
```

### Testing Commands

```bash
# Fast local testing (Chromium only)
npx test-storybook --url http://localhost:6006 --browsers chromium

# All browsers
npx test-storybook --url http://localhost:6006 --browsers chromium firefox webkit

# Update snapshots
npx test-storybook --url http://localhost:6006 --browsers chromium --updateSnapshot

# Via Wireit
npm run test:storybook
npm run test:storybook:all
npm run test:storybook:update
```

### Existing Test Commands

```bash
# Unit tests (Jest/Stencil)
npm test
npm run test:coverage
npm run test:update-snapshot
npm run test:watch
```

