## Troubleshooting

### Issue 1: Storybook server not starting

```bash
# Check if port is in use (Windows)
netstat -ano | findstr :6006

# Start with different port
npx storybook dev --port 6007
```

### Issue 2: Playwright browsers not installed

```bash
npx playwright install
npx playwright install chromium
```

### Issue 3: Web component not rendering in test

Web components render asynchronously. Use `findBy*` queries:
```typescript
// Wrong
const el = canvas.getByRole('button');

// Correct
const el = await canvas.findByRole('button');
```

### Issue 4: Custom events not captured

Stencil custom events need direct event listeners:
```typescript
const el = await canvas.findByRole('button');
const eventPromise = new Promise(resolve => {
  el.addEventListener('buttonClick', resolve, { once: true });
});
await userEvent.click(el);
await eventPromise;
```

