## Safety Boundaries

### Files the Agent CAN Create/Modify:

✅ `.storybook/test-runner.ts` (new)
✅ `playwright.config.ts` (new)
✅ `.storybook/main.ts` (add interactions addon)
✅ `package.json` (Wireit targets, devDependencies)
✅ `*.stories.ts` files (add play functions)
✅ `COMPONENT_TEST_MATRIX.md` (new)
✅ `TESTING_GUIDE.md` (new)

### Files the Agent MUST NOT Modify:

❌ Component implementation files (`modus-wc-*.tsx`)
❌ Component styles (`modus-wc-*.scss`)
❌ `stencil.config.ts`
❌ `tsconfig.json`
❌ `.gitignore`
❌ Any files outside the project

